---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Supplement Hero"
	description="How Supplement Hero handles plain-language supplement coverage and scheduled publishing."
	pubDate={new Date('March 24 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		Supplement Hero is a consumer-facing publication that translates supplement research into
		plain-language guidance for readers who want more signal and less hype.
	</p>
	<p>
		Each article moves through editorial review before it is marked approved in the content
		frontmatter. Astro pages, RSS, and individual post routes only expose entries whose publish time
		has passed, which lets the team queue posts ahead of time.
	</p>
	<p>
		The goal is not to make treatment decisions for readers. The publication explains evidence
		strength, common marketing tactics, uncertainty, and the kinds of questions a reader should take
		back to a clinician when stakes are high.
	</p>
</Layout>
